dataList.title: Bloodfiend
dataList.content: Unbelievable... My first Kindred to be created without their authorization... is this bumbling fool...?

dataList.title: Bloodfiend
dataList.content: I pray for your forgiveness... My parent...

dataList.title: Bloodfiend
dataList.content: ... Begone from my sight. At least thou hast brought me Bloodbags for sustenance...

dataList.title: Bloodfiend
dataList.content: Yet, it must be the responsibility of a parent to clean up the mess of his child...
With that, Cassetti reached out toward the pile of Bloodbags on the ground, and...

dataList.title: Bloodfiend
dataList.content: Haah... Oh, what abundance... I had nearly forgotten this sensation...
An armor of hardened blood materialized over the Bloodfiend's body; his sheer aggression and hatred was palpable enough to make our skin crawl.
... It appears that he has empowered himself by reaping their blood.

dataList.title: Bloodfiend
dataList.content: Though my power is yet to fully return... This magnificent armor is quite befitting of a parade for the prince who hath become a king! Wouldst thou agree? Yessir, yes you do! 'Course you do!

dataList.title: Bloodfiend
dataList.content: Challenge me now, o rebels! Challenge thy king!
